---
import DocsLayout from 'project:layouts/docs/docs-layout.astro'
import AstroToolkitPPTPurchaseButton from 'project:components/astro-toolkit-ppt-purchase-button/astro-toolkit-ppt-purchase-button.astro'
import Heading from 'project:components/astro-headings/heading.astro'
import AstroToolkitPPTPurchaseDialog from 'project:components/astro-toolkit-ppt-purchase-dialog/astro-toolkit-ppt-purchase-dialog.astro'
const content = {
	title: 'Astro Toolkit for Microsoft PowerPoint',
	description: `Introducing the Astro PowerPoint Toolkit: Streamline wireframing for space and intelligence professionals in secure environments.`,
}
---

<DocsLayout content={content} file={import.meta.url}>
	<!-- Putting custom styles in a style tag like this is Astro.js's recommendation -->
	<style>
		.p-astro-toolkit-ppt_image {
			/* Layout */
			margin-block-end: 7--step;

			/* Layout */
			margin-block-start: 7--step;

			& img {
				/* Layout */
				margin-block-end: 9--step;
				max-inline-size: 100%;
			}

			& p {
				/* Text */
				font-size: 0.875rem;
			}
		}

		.p-astro-toolkit-ppt {
			&small {
				display: flex;
			}
		}
	</style>
	<Heading type="h2" title="Product Details" />
	<p>
		In the aerospace and defense industry, software restrictions can pose
		challenges when it comes to wireframing in certain environments. That's why
		we've developed the Astro PowerPoint Toolkit, a solution tailored
		specifically for space and intelligence workers to use in the most secure
		and restricted environments.
	</p>
	<AstroToolkitPPTPurchaseButton showTerms={true} />
	<div class="p-astro-toolkit-ppt_image">
		<img
			src="/images/astro-toolkit-ppt-screen-1.png"
			alt="Astro toolkit ppt screen 1"
			loading="lazy"
			width="635"
			height="353"
		/>
		<p>
			The Astro Toolkit enables rapid, DoD-approved wireframing for streamlined
			design and validation.
		</p>
	</div>

	<p>
		<strong>The Astro PowerPoint Toolkit&nbsp;</strong>offers a lightweight and
		DoD-approved medium for rapid wireframing. It leverages familiar PowerPoint
		software, widely used in the industry, to provide a seamless integration
		into existing workflows. This means that designers, developers, and product
		teams can quickly create and validate wireframes, even in environments where
		time and access to other design tools are limited.
	</p>

	<div class="p-astro-toolkit-ppt_image">
		<img
			src="/images/astro-toolkit-ppt-screen-2.png"
			alt="Astro toolkit ppt screen 2"
			loading="lazy"
			width="512"
			height="434"
		/>
		<p>
			The toolkit provides core components for quickly customizing your space
			app designs with drag-and-drop ease.
		</p>
	</div>
	<Heading type="h2" title="Features" />

	<ul>
		<li>
			Core Astro design system: The toolkit includes the essential components of
			the Astro design system, ensuring consistency and efficiency in
			wireframing.
		</li>
		<li>
			Authorized and familiar medium: By leveraging the power of PowerPoint,
			professionals can seamlessly integrate wireframing into their existing
			workflows.
		</li>
		<li>
			Effort reduction: Reduced prototyping design time by 75%, allowing teams
			to focus on innovation and collaboration.
		</li>
	</ul>

	<Heading type="h2" title="License Types" />

	<p>
		There are four types of license for the Astro PPT Toolkit.
	</p>

	<ul>
		<li>
			<b>$49 Individual License</b>
			<br />For use by an individual
		</li>
		<li>
			<b>$175 Team License</b>
			<br />For up to five individual users for a single project
		</li>
		<li>
			<b>$250 Project License</b>
			<br />Unlimited users for a single, specified project for one of your clients or an internal client
		</li>
		<li>
			<b>Enterprise License</b>
			<br />Unlimited users in an organization for multiple projects. Please contact <a href="mailto:support@astrouxds.com>support@astrouxds.com</a> for more information.
		</li>
	</ul>

	<Heading type="h2" title="Purchase Astro Toolkit" />

	<AstroToolkitPPTPurchaseButton showTerms={true} />

	<AstroToolkitPPTPurchaseDialog />
</DocsLayout>
